  "page": "Elia",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The name <b>Elia</b> may refer to one of the following characters:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Martell\" title=\"Elia Martell\">Elia Martell</a>, the sister of Prince Doran and Prince Oberyn Martell.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Sand\" title=\"Elia Sand\">Elia Sand</a>, the eldest bastard daughter of Prince Oberyn Martell by his long-time paramour Ellaria Sand.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Elia&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ella_Broome\" title=\"Ella Broome\">Ella Broome</a>, the good-sister of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Prentys_Tully\" title=\"Prentys Tully\">Prentys Tully</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ella_Lannister\" title=\"Ella Lannister\">Ella Lannister</a>, the wife of <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Lannister_(son_of_Jason)\" title=\"Damon Lannister (son of Jason)\">Damon Lannister</a>.</li>\n<li>A slave from Meereen called either <a href=\"/index.php/Elza\" title=\"Elza\">Elza</a> or Ella.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404160755\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key we